/**
 * Cross-cutting concerns shared across all modules.
 *
 * Structure:
 * - decorators/    @CurrentUser, @HotelId, @Permissions, @Public
 * - filters/       HttpExceptionFilter, PrismaExceptionFilter
 * - guards/        JwtAuthGuard, RolesGuard, PermissionsGuard, TenantGuard
 * - interceptors/  TransformInterceptor, LoggingInterceptor, TimeoutInterceptor
 * - middleware/    TenantResolverMiddleware, RequestIdMiddleware
 * - pipes/         ParseHotelIdPipe, ZodValidationPipe
 * - constants/     Role names, permission keys, error codes
 * - types/         RequestWithUser, AuthenticatedUser
 * - utils/         Pagination helpers, date utilities
 * - dto/           PaginationDto, ApiResponseDto
 */
